value.name: Margo's Got Money Troubles
value.overview: Margo Millet, the child of a Hooters waitress and an ex-pro wrestler, becomes pregnant after a brief affair with an English professor, Mark, at the local junior college she attends. Now, at 20, Margo is alone with an infant, unemployed, and on the verge of eviction. When her estranged father Jinx shows up on her doorstep and asks to move in with her, she agrees in exchange for help with childcare. Margo starts an OnlyFans as an experiment and soon finds herself adapting some of Jinx’s advice from the world of wrestling. Could this be the answer to all of Margo’s problems, or does internet fame come with too high a price?
